1976da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/BzyKcy7gb_P/?igshid=12dnhtwaefqw9</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T19:20:38.000Z","msg":"連儂牆目的係發聲<br />\n希望大家唔好有個心想教化藍絲而去太危險既區域<br />\n佢地唔會聽得明"},{"pid":"93cd51a77090a243edede8ba75bac060a91ea3a7","tid":1308030,"uid":266578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T19:22:32.000Z","msg":"認同push"},{"pid":"69580037741f449ecdfcd771e8fa06201a93a62d","tid":1308030,"uid":97162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T19:25:44.000Z","msg":"行到邊貼到邊得幾張啲師奶反而會望一兩眼<br />\n又可以鼓勵自己人遍地開花<br />\n反感既見到你一大幅牆已經知咩料直行直過甚至破壞啦"},{"pid":"f7b72251336172e3f60499b8f7a5312f94b037a3","tid":1308030,"uid":97162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T19:28:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2a253e054e494a8ebcfa3473a81ad6651e2d7dbc","tid":1308030,"uid":97162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T19:28:54.000Z","msg":"每一個人都可以係流動連儂人"},{"pid":"f395489666d2b6a231a13a10c2d0c6bc59def63a","tid":1308030,"uid":97162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T19:33:47.000Z","msg":"有心搞破壞既藍絲廢老<br />\n佢地最大目標唔係幅牆<br />\n而係整呢幅牆既廢青<br />\nbe water 唔好比機會佢地"},{"pid":"dd927353e189fc993444b143f96affcf712697f3","tid":1308030,"uid":97162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T19:35:16.000Z","msg":"會係街企係到寫memo既好多都係路過既市民<br />\n大部分都係和理非<br />\n你想還拖分分鐘比人屌返轉頭<br />\n佢地唔會陪你癲"},{"pid":"cc70812b44b25de418fd99c249f6be6ed625b0a0","tid":1308030,"uid":97162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T19:36:16.000Z","msg":"見到隔離北角連儂牆post<br />\n我唔想再有人受傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8ac048966158932d2411fdde4d82549abfde497","tid":1308030,"uid":97162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T19:53:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"080b71003b38104af821126f63ba04250f0